Planigle is a Ruby on Rails based agile planning application. It was developed by and is copyrighted by
Walter Bodwell (2008-2012).  It is licensed under GPLv2 (included in this distribution).  All rights to the
Planigle logo are reserved.  It is not permitted to use the Planigle logo outside the scope of this
application.

