iui (CSS and Images for iPhone) - Free (minimal restrictions; see license file)
rails-iui (Rails Plugin) - MIT
Cairngorm (Flex library) - BSD
Flex automation libraries - MPL (included for build convenience; part of Flex SDK)
Icons - http://www.visual-blast.com/graphics/icons/free-web-application-icons-set/ - Free (no restrictions)
